{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You just received a love letter! But it's written with codes... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To read it you will need to solve the puzzles and get codes, which will serve to reveal the words of the letter. Each code is a word. Can you decipher what is written in the letter?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your <strong>mouse or arrow keys</strong> to draw the line. Fill the entire board and solve the puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/GIF_1.gif?t=1737130693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Did something wrong? You can <strong>go back easily.</strong> Or just <strong>right click</strong> to delete the line wherever you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/GIF_5.gif?t=1737130693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After solving the puzzle you will get a <strong>code.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/GIF_3.gif?t=1737130693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Find the code</strong> on the letter and <strong>discover</strong> the secret word.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/GIF_4.gif?t=1737130693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No tutorial. <strong>Straight to the game</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Minimalist design</strong>. No score, timer or pressure. Solve the puzzle in your ti